				<span class="prof">
						Junior AX Developer в <a class="company" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/smart-business/" target="_blank"><span class="company-favicon" style="background: url(https://s.dou.ua/img/static/favicons/sm.png) no-repeat;">SMART business</span></a>
