							<div class="g-avatar">	<img src="https://s.dou.ua/img/avatars/40x40_profilepicturekronova.jpg" user="273693" title="Oksana Kronova" width="40" height="40" alt="Oksana Kronova" srcset="https://s.dou.ua/img/avatars/80x80_profilepicturekronova.jpg 1.1x">
